data.description: Introducing this charming 2 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath home with over 1200 sq ft of living space.  Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and the beach, you'll have endless opportunities to enjoy the sun and surf.  The backyard boasts a vinyl fence, providing privacy and security for outdoor gatherings or peaceful relaxation.  Plenty of room for a pool!  What makes this home even more applealing is the emergency generator that kicks in when power goes out, ensuring peace of mind during any unforeseen circumstances. The Belle Vista neighborhood also contains multiple waterfront parks and playgrounds. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to own a beacutiful home in this desirable location.
